loggin to proxmox
go to local (prox)
down to ct templates
downlaod from template from url or upload
create ct in top right
untick unprivleged container
set hostname and password
select greencloud.tar.zst from templates
select defaults
network set to dhcp
and finish
 edit container config /etc/pve/lxc/<container id>.conf
  # ==== GreenCloud runtime permissions ====
  lxc.cap.drop:
  lxc.apparmor.profile: unconfined
  lxc.cgroup2.devices.allow: a
  lxc.mount.auto: proc:rw sys:rw
  lxc.mount.entry: /dev/fuse dev/fuse none bind,create=file 0 0
start the conatiner
on the host, enter the conatiner - pct enter <conatinerid>
in root, run configure_node.sh
